      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/trump-fed-seen-risking-127-billion-bond-spree-in-latin-america</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲借款人以三年来最快的速度涌入全球市场的债务出售热潮预计将在 2025 年逐渐消退。]]></description>
